Telluride

Telluride, Colorado is a small town in the heart of the Rocky Mountains. 
It's well known for it's beautiful view, waterfalls, ski resort, and hiking 
experiences. Although small, this town has a warm heart of gold with a 
welcoming community that can make any trip a memorable vacation. The site 
should be designed to encourage and inspire people to visit by providing
well researched information and photos to capture its beauty.